    "data": "بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْم\nاَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ الَّذِىْ اَذْهَبَ الَّيْلَ مُظْلِمًا بِقُدْرَتِهٖ وَ جَآءَ بِالنَّهَارِ مُبْصِرًا بِرَحْمَتِهٖ وَ كَسَانِىْ ضِيَآئَهٗ وَ اَنَا فِىْ نِعْمَتِهٖ اَللّٰهُمَّ فَكَمَا اَبْقَيْتَنِىْ لَهٗ فَاَبْقِنِىْ لِاَمْثَالِهٖ وَ صَلِّ عَلَى النَّبِىِّ مُحَمَّدٍ وَ آلِهٖ وَ لَا تَفْجَعْنِىْ فِيْهِ وَ فِىْ غَيْرِهٖ مِنَ اللَّيَالِىْ وَالْاَيَّامِ بِارْتِكَابِ الْمَحَارِمِ وَاكْتِسَابِ الْمَآثِمِ وَارْزُقْنِىْ خَيْرَهُ وَ خَيْرَ مَا فِيْهِ وَ خَيْرَ مَا بَعْدَهٗ وَاصْرِفْ عَنِّىْ شَرَّهٗ وَ شَرَّ مَا فِيْهِ وَ شَرَّ مَا بَعْدَهٗ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّىْ بِذِمَّةِ الْاِسْلاَمِ اَتَوَسَّلُ اِلَيْكَ وَ بِحُرْمَةِ الْقُرْاٰنِ اَعْتَمِدُ عَلَيْكَ وَ بِمُحَمَّدِ نِ الْمُصْطَفٰى صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهٖ اَسْتَشْفِعُ لَدَيْكَ فَاعْرِفِ اللّٰهُمَّ ذِمَّتِىَ الَّتِىْ رَجَوْتُ بِهَا قَضَآءَ حَاجَتِىْ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ اَللّٰهُمَّ اقْضِ لِىْ فِىْ الْخَمِيْسِ خَمْسًا لَا يَتَّسِعُ لَهَا اِلَّا كَرَمُكَ وَ لَا يُطِيْقُهَا اِلَّا نِعَمُكَ سَلاَمَةً اَقْوٰى بِهَا عَلٰى طَاعَتِكَ وَ عِبَادَةً اَسْتَحِقُّ بِهَا جَزِيْلَ مَثُوْبَتِكَ وَسَعَةً فِى الْحَالِ مِنَ الرِّزْقِ الْحَلاَلِ وَ اَنْ تُؤْمِنَنِىْ فِىْ مَوَقِفِ الْخَوْفِ بِاَمْنِكَ وَ تَجْعَلَنِىْ مِنْ طَواَرِقِ الْهُمُوْمِ وَالْغُمُوْمِ فِىْ حِصْنِكَ وَ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاجْعَلْ تَوَسُّلِىْ بِهٖ شَافِعًا يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ نَافِعًا اِنَّكَ اَنْتَ اَرْحَمُ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ.\nBISMIL LAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM. ALHAMDO LILLAAHIL LAZEE AZHARAL LAYLA MUZLEMAN BE-QUDRATEHI WA JAAA-A BIN-NAHAARE MUBSERAN BE-RAHMATEHI WA KASAANEE ZEYAAA-AHU WA ANAA FEE NEA’MATEHI ALLAAHUMMA FA-KAMAA ABQAYTANEE LAHU FA ABQENEE LE-AMSAALEHEE WA SALLE A’LAN NABIYYE MOHAMMADIN WA AALEHI WA LAA TAFJA’-NEE FEEHE WA FEE GHAYREHEE MENAL LAYAALEE WAL AYYAAME BIR-TEKAABIL MAHAAREME WAKTESAABIL MAAA-SEME WAR-ZUQNEE KHAYRAHU WA KHAYRA MAA FEEHE WA KHAYRA MAA BA’-DAHU WASRIF A’NNEE SHARRAHU WA SHARRA MAA FEEHE WA SHARRA MAA BA’-DAHUALLAAHUMMA INNEE BE-ZIMMATIL ISLAAME ATAWASSALO ELAYKA WA BEHURMATIL QUR-AANE A-A’TAMEDO A’LAYKA WA BE MOHAMMADENIL MUSTAFAA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI ASTASHFE-O’ LADAYKA FA’REFIL LAAHUMMA ZIMMATEYAL LATEE RAJAWTO BEHAA QAZAAA-A HAAJATEE YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEEN ALLAHUMMAQ ZE LEE FIL KHAMEESE KHAMSAN LAA YATTASE-O’ LAHAA ILLAA KARAMOKA WA LAA YOTEEQOHAA ILLAA NE-A’MOKA SALAAMATAN AQWAA BEHAA A’LAA TAA-A’TEKA WA E’BAADATAN ASTAHIQQO BEHA JAZEELA MASOOBATEKA WA SA-A’TAN FIL HAALE MENAR RIZQIL HALAALE WA AN TOA-MENANEE FEE MAWAQEFIL KHAWFE BE AMNEKA WA TAJ-A’LANEE MIN TAWAAREQIL HOMOOME WAL GHOMOOME FEE HISNEKA WA SALLE ALAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIWNWAJ-A’L TAWASSOLEE BEHEE SHAAFE-A’N YAWMAL QEYAAMATE NAAFE-A’N INNAKA ANTA ARHAMUR RAAHEMEEN.\nIn the Name of Allah, the All-merciful, the All-compassionate Praise belongs to Allah, who has taken away the shadowy night by His power and brought the sight-giving day through His mercy. He has clothed me in its brightness and given me its favour. O Allah, just as Youhave spared me for this day, so also spare me for its likes, bless the prophet Muhammad and his Household, torment me not in it and in other nights and days by allowing me to commit unlawful acts and to clothe myself in sins; provide me with this good, the good of all within it, and the good of everything after it; and turn away from me its evil, the evil of all within it, and the evil of everything after it! O Allah, by the protective compact of Islam, I seek mediation with You! By the inviolability of the Qur’an, I rely upon You! By Muhammad the chosen (Allah bless him and his Household) I seek intercession with You! So recognize my protective compact by which I hope my need will be granted, O Most Merciful of the merciful! O Allah, decree for me on Thursday five things which none embraces but Your generosity and none supports but Your favours: health through which I may have the strength to obey You, worship by which I may deserve Your plentiful reward, plenty in my state through lawful provision, and that You makest me secure in the places of fear through Your security, and placest me in Your fortress against the striking of worries and sorrows! Bless Muhammad and his Household, and make my seeking his mediation as an intercessor give profit on the Day of Resurrection! Surely Youare the Most Merciful of the merciful! ", 
    "title": "The Supplication of Thursday"
